yle=\"font-size: small;\">除非話佩狗一早計好哂啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條柒碌有幾撚好啊 睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多咪好過賓蛇些少"}]}